Name: Marduk-šumu-ibni
ind.Name: Marduk-šumu-ibni

Father of Nabû-balassu-iqbi (Nabû-bullissu), {{f}}Amat-Nanāya, {{f}}Amat-Ninlil and {{f}}Binunu. Grandfather of Libluṭ/Nabû-balāssu-iqbi.
